data.description: This stunning 7-bedroom, 4-full bathroom home with captivating brick accents, nestled in the prestigious Chapel Hill area, invites you to experience a tranquil lifestyle. Step onto the inviting brick porch, ideal for enjoying your morning coffee. Upon entering, the home exudes an open and welcoming atmosphere, cleverly designed with the steps positioned away from the front door. Discover distinct dining and living spaces, with the versatility for the living room to easily transform into a home office. The spacious kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring a top-notch stainless steel package with a cooktop, oven, microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator. Enhancing the kitchen's charm are the island, and breakfast bar, creating a cozy ambiance. The master bedroom and bathroom provide a personal sanctuary, whirlpool tub, separate shower, double vanities, and a spacious walk-in closet. Don't miss the opportunity to explore this home and call it yours today!
